        "ROB_RAVAGER_BODY_THROW_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "En tant que Ravageur, consommez 8 ennemis ou plus à la fois.",
        "ROB_RAVAGER_BODY_BEAM_UNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Ravager: Calm as an Ocean",
